in models]]\n[[Category:Brazilian health activists]]\n[[Category:Victoria's Secret Angels]]\n", "name_user": "Trillfendi", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eCharitable activities", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gisele_B%C3%BCndchen"}
